cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper focuses on sentiment analysis on user reviews, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel constrained convex optimization framework, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with sentiment analysis on textual data, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
